<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3689282>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. Pycnoides zambiaensis n. sp.: A, holotype male habitus; B, holotype male dorsum; C, holotype male timbal; D, paratype male operculum; E, paratype male lateral view of genitalia; F, paratype male posterior view of genitalia. Scale bar: A, 2 cm; B, 5 mm; C—F, 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3689282/files/figure.png" ;
